{"tid":1294532,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"到依家都仲有人用母子嚟比喻政府同人民，我真係屌你老母","createTime":"2019-07-07T19:38:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T16:27:47.000Z","uid":163171,"like":81,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"3a4d35c3bb31287dd273f350cea8a8997033740d","tid":1294532,"uid":163171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T19:38:37.000Z","msg":"一個民主社會，政府從來都係人民公僕；人民有權利同義務監督政府嘅施政同執法。假如一個政府立惡法、縱容執法者濫權，而激起民憤，佢好應該被問責同時向大眾回應訴求；呢個過程同母子關係、權力階級完全無關。<br />\n<br />\n我發覺有極多港豬潛意識入面仲係有 &ldquo;阿爺〞&ldquo;阿媽〞呢種錯誤觀念，乞求、妄想權貴會施捨民主，係時候要屌醒佢地。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">還政於民！</span></span>"},{"pid":"75470e489675695f2681be0bf65ebc37008be3ff","tid":1294532,"uid":163171,"like":1,"dislike":18,"score":-17,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T19:39:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bMzph9k.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbMzph9k.png&h=424db311&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"58b02fb4492dffdf39885705e75f02403a247c52","tid":1294532,"uid":163171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T19:43:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da067832923b0611557ab8a865fa95bb8db8a272","tid":1294532,"uid":163171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T19:51:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca1de331a4e03922f13c2c79064c5532a1980492","tid":1294532,"uid":163171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T20:09:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"039ba096d330bb5bc5843dc264d0628ccf93a6b4","tid":1294532,"uid":144865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T20:17:01.000Z","msg":"其實母子係啱嫁喎<br />\n人民係母<br />\n政府係子"},{"pid":"3fa39aff748ff925a9be22abd5279fe1c71da4b9","tid":1294532,"uid":144865,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"039ba096d330bb5bc5843dc264d0628ccf93a6b4","tid":1294532,"uid":144865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T20:17:01.000Z","msg":"其實母